    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cow's Milk holds the cosmic power of the universe!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The alien queen demands you bring back power for the colony. Escort cows out of every level. Just make sure not to get caught.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras/77c944b7a1732dd6926d8cde6a2c71d6.avif?t=1734129526\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras_big/77c944b7a1732dd6926d8cde6a2c71d6.avif?t=1734129526 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras/f45320602a68d17fc662849091e29504.avif?t=1734129526\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras_big/f45320602a68d17fc662849091e29504.avif?t=1734129526 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use gadgets to outsmart the farmers and avoid detection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras/d4b47e6b1946e9e5c601addfa1d8e3d6.avif?t=1734129526\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras_big/d4b47e6b1946e9e5c601addfa1d8e3d6.avif?t=1734129526 width=800 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras/fa04274fd3b6fd87bd53c2f6729622f6.avif?t=1734129526\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras_big/fa04274fd3b6fd87bd53c2f6729622f6.avif?t=1734129526 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get golds on every level to appease the queen and bring honor to your colony!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras/f210e399e91cf2d776804d68e549f852.avif?t=1734129526\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244180/extras_big/f210e399e91cf2d776804d68e549f852.avif?t=1734129526 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
